item.title: CVE-2022-4368|2024-08-03T01:34:50.163Z -- unknown -- wp%20csv
item.description: The WP CSV WordPress plugin through 1.8.0.0 does not sanitize and escape a parameter before outputting it back in the page when importing a CSV, and doe snot have CSRF checks in place as well, leading to a Reflected Cross-Site Scripting.
